{"tid":983705,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"英文作文elective(debating)一問","createTime":"2019-01-16T07:37:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-20T14:51:04.000Z","uid":143869,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1d4fb83147ece3e3b5a79f1a864b601402473f6a","tid":983705,"uid":143869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T07:37:35.000Z","msg":"小弟正準備2019DSE<br />\n之前英文作極都係 Workplace Communication, Social Issues &amp; Popular Culture<br />\n呢3個elective 大約都係11至14(over 21分)<br />\n<br />\n我想試下作debating既文俾補習老師改<br />\n但我發覺我補果個好似唔教格式同用字咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我想問下debate 呢個elective<br />\n係咪有 Type1: debate speech類 <span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>[The motion/task is:xxxxxxxx. for or against]</strong></span> <br />\n同 Type2: 議論文argumentative類 <strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">[Letter to the editor/article + 3reasons]</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n咁我應唔應該作debating既文?(我未學過格式同用字 <strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">唔知係咪</span></strong>有專用格式同用字)<br />\n我可唔可以當佢係argumentative writing咁寫?<br />\n<br />\n有無巴絲可以講俾我知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nThank you"},{"pid":"e03f4589d358b6eafeccf1ba91708b5ed782e3f5","tid":983705,"uid":143869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T15:05:26.000Z","msg":"推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fede97c3aa51b592c9d3101a072c462bda4d8251","tid":983705,"uid":143869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T22:40:21.000Z","msg":"推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d5cdd89eca7813de7aa80c177caac57d908197b","tid":983705,"uid":140664,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T22:53:55.000Z","msg":"佢跟本同argumentative 冇咩分別既<br />\n只係可能要寫得有說服力 同埋要立場同語氣堅定<br />\n例如 it is indisputable that....<br />\nUndoubtedly/not r&eacute;futable etc etc"},{"pid":"da4ff61f06aa983289fa36